com.mapbox.services.android.navigation.v5.navigation

Class NavigationRoute

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapbox.services.android.navigation.v5.navigation.NavigationRoute

  • public final class NavigationRoute
extends Object
    The NavigationRoute class wraps the MapboxDirections class with parameters which must be set in order for a navigation session to successfully begin. While it is possible to pass in any DirectionsRoute into MapboxNavigation.startNavigation(DirectionsRoute), using this class will ensure your request includes all the proper information needed for the navigation session to begin.

    Developer Note: MapboxDirections cannot be directly extended since it is an AutoValue class.

    0.5.0
